data.description: WHAT A DEAL !!!! Price dramatically improved for a quick sale. Buyers, your dream for homeownership is here !!! This AMAZING home, that has been loved for and cared for the past 10 years, is calling YOUR name. You don't want to miss this phenomenal starter home located in THE LAKES in PORT RICHEY, FL! As you step inside, you'll be welcomed by beautiful LUXURIOUS VINYL PLANK FLOORS sprawling throughout. You will be amazed at how open and spacious this home is. All of the essentials have been addressed in the past 10 years. New Roof, New AC  and Ductwork, as well as windows, garage door opener and many other upgrades were done in 2013. Recent updates include new floors, paint, upgraded exterior paver patio, privacy fence and many other features. This home features 2 very spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths and 2 car garage. Both rooms are located separate from each other for maximum privacy. All bathrooms are spacious and just need your personal touches to give them a more modern look. Plenty of space to roam with almost 1,400 sq/ft of living space. If you love to entertain, this is the HOME for YOU. Your home features living and dining areas as well as a massive family room off the kitchen, with a beautiful accent wall where the wood fire burning fireplace is located. The kitchen is super spacious and would be soo appreciated by the chef in the family. Plenty of cabinets and counter space for cooking , storage and entertaining. All modern appliances complement the look.  Off your family room, you have access to a very ample enclosed lanai where you will surely spend a lot of time enjoying your favorite drink; whether it is a warm cup of tea or coffee in the mornings, or some cool drink in the afternoon. If you would like more adventure, then step outside to enjoy your massive extended patio where you could enjoy your fire pit all year long, or maybe take on gardening. This home is perfect for a first time home buyer, or an investor looking for a great income producing opportunity. No deed or rental restrictions (as long as in line with county ordinances), No CDD, affordable taxes and NO Flood insurance.  This home is conveniently located just minutes away from Little Rd, Embassy Blvd, and Highway 19, where you will find an array of shopping, restaurants, healthcare facilities, stunning beaches and easy access to major highways. Commuting to Tarpon Springs, Trinity, Clearwater, or Downtown Tampa is a breeze, making this home a perfect choice for those seeking a harmonious blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Down Payment assistance programs available for first time home buyers. Please contact us for more details and to schedule your private showing today.
